# Description
Get the latest weather data for any region in the world.

# Features
You can all details for your given area like
1)cloud_pct
2)temperature
3)feels_like
4)humidity
5)min_temp
6)max_temp
7)wind_speed
8)wind_degrees
9)sunrise
10)sunset
